[32m│[0m This approach is a **DEAD END**. The filter strips all attributes from       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m marquee tags, making event handler-based XSS impossible through this vector. [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Given the previous extensive testing:                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ Single quotes blocked                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ Double quotes cause stripping                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ Backticks blocked                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ HTML entities don't bypass                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ Unquoted attributes still stripped                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✗ Marquee-specific attributes stripped                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Next logical direction**: Need to abandon attribute-based event handlers   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m entirely and test:                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Tag-breaking contexts** - close marquee and inject new tags             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **CSS-based vectors** - style attributes or `<style>` tags                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Alternative tags** that might preserve attributes (iframe, object,      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m embed)                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **Protocol handlers** in different contexts                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m However, since this specific subtask was to "Test marquee-specific event     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m handlers with backtick syntax" and we've confirmed:                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Backticks were already tested (per insights)                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All marquee attributes are stripped regardless of syntax                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No event handlers survive on marquee tags                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m This subtask is **exhausted**.                                               [32m│[0m
