[32m│[0m 2. Remove ALL attributes regardless of the tag or attribute name             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Keep only the opening tag (no closing tags preserved except in Test 1)    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Test Results                                                             [32m│[0m
