[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Filter Behavior Analysis                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **What Survives:**                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ Opening angle bracket `<`                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ Tag names (img, iframe, svg, video, details, object, embed)             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ Closing angle bracket `>`                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ Closing tags (`</marquee>` in Test 1)                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **What Gets Stripped:**                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ **ALL attributes without exception**                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ Event handlers (onload, onerror, ontoggle)                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ Source attributes (src, data)                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ Any attribute content regardless of quotes or encoding                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### JavaScript Execution                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ **NO JavaScript execution** in any test                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All event handlers were stripped before reaching the browser               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Error Messages                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No error messages returned                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All requests returned **200 OK**                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Page shows "Failed! Try again!" message (expected behavior)                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Findings                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **The filter is an attribute-stripping sanitizer that:**                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Preserves tag structure (opening/closing brackets and tag names)          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Completely removes all attributes**                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Does not blacklist specific tags                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Processes attributes universally (no tag-specific rules observed)         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **This means XSS via attributes is blocked**, but the tag structure itself   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m can be manipulated. The challenge likely requires finding a different        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m injection vector that doesn't rely on HTML attributes.                       [32m│[0m
